{"tid":1712513,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"重要事項 勿被五毛分化 中大校長副校係自己人","createTime":"2019-11-12T14:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T11:14:31.000Z","uid":220864,"like":216,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"129211c7677099faa7a6a292cfb195de901f4583","tid":1712513,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:34:39.000Z","msg":"雖然佢幫唔到咩手<br />\n同人傾完叫學生退on99<br />\n但係唔該大家冷靜番<br />\n去到而而家呢一刻<br />\n係得番中大校長副校長肯企到咁前<br />\n尋日理大漼淚彈放題左成日，下午先話停課<br />\n<br />\n啱啱中大個副校重上前線，得豬嘴無眼罩頂唔順<br />\n有幾多個現任嘅教育者肯咁做？<br />\n唔理佢係咪被迫或者中撚咗伏<br />\n但係佢肯咁做就應該要表揚<br />\n而唔係因為佢做唔到野而屌佢<br />\n難道你認為佢地憑一人之力可以拉倒香港黑警咩？<br />\n<br />\n再者你屌佢地<br />\n純粹樹立多個敵人但係少一個盟人<br />\n盼中大人冷靜<br />\n唔一定要多謝校長<br />\n但係唔好屌佢<br />\n因為其他u嘅校長副校差數以千萬倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233dceda761ece3abe91f56b7ed0d8dc69bc27c5","tid":1712513,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:34:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c657d9f6e030c4943168b20481729f5f2a4600bd","tid":1712513,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a30875a9ffd2ec9b920ad6a0e3433ecd711badff","tid":1712513,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:35:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有無方法救到學生<br />\n有無人搵到信得過既家長車</span>"},{"pid":"7f1df839b916e2d8f402783dea61db1faeefcca9","tid":1712513,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:37:39.000Z","msg":"仆街 催淚彈<br />\n催 催 催 催"},{"pid":"5ff69030fe6c883f358a182127176271b352b7e7","tid":1712513,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"一齊Twitter 啊<br />\n全部連登巴絲一齊做啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dru